    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 for MRL 2. Experimental validation demonstrates RH < 1 at all 5 operating points with prediction error within ±15 %. UQ campaign (reported in validation narrative) confirms 95th-percentile RH = 0.97 < 1.0 acceptance criterion. The computational model is accepted as fit for purpose for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
